
Database information

Table: Katalog_gemeinde
        Name of community - name
        id of the community - gemeinde_id : unique number
 
Table: katalog_stoff

        stoff_nr - substance number
        Name - name of the substance
        Beschreibung - explanation of the substance
        
        Knowing the unique number of the substances that are useful to us
        Nitrat - 1244
        Nitrat-stickstoff - 1245
        Nitrit - 1246
        Nitrit-stickstoff- 1247
        
Table: open_messstelle
        sl_nr - technical key number : primary key used as foreign key on other tables
        messstelle_id - unique number  used as foreign key in other tables
        name- messstelle name- measuring point name
        e32- location of the east or east co-ordinates
        N32 - location on the north or north co-ordinates
        gw_stockwerk: 
        Grundstück - type of land
        gemeinde_id - connects with katalog_gemeinde
        gwhorizont_id - ground water horizon
        gwhorizont - ground water
        gwleiter_id - aquifer id
        gwleiter - aquifer
        einrichtungsgrund - reason for implementation of messstelle
        gwk_lage_auf_id - groundwater map
        gwk_lage_id-
        gwk_monitoring_auf_id-
        gwk_monitoring_id-
        messprogramm- measurement programm
        turnus_wasserstand - regular water cycle frequency
        freigabe_wstd- availability of  water level datas
        freigabe_chemie - chemistry datas
        freigabe_lage - position of well
        wasserstandsmessstelle - water level measuring point
        gütemessstelle - quality measuring point
        im_wrrl_messnetz_wasserstand - measuring point waterframework directive(waterlevel)
        im_wrrl_messnetz_chemie - measuring point waterframework directive(chemistry)
        messstellenart - measuring point type
        wasserart - water type
        labor - laboratory type
        beobachtung_wassertand - waterlevel observation
        eigentümer- owner
        betreiber - operator
        filterlänge - filter length
        sumpfrohrlänge - sump pipe length
        ausbaudurchmesser - removal diameter
        historischer_ruhe_wsp - 
        einbaulänge - installation length
        oberkante filter - top edge filter
        unterkante filter - lower egde filter
        
        
        
Table: open_messwert

        messstelle_id - measuring place id.... connects open_messwert
        pna_id - sampling id
        datum_pn - time and date
        stoff_nr - substance number
        probengut - sample good
        messergebnis_c - measurement result
        messergebnis_hinweis - measurement result note
        bestimmungsgrenze - Limit of quantitation
        masseinheit - unit of measurement
        trennverfahren - separation process
        verfahren - procedure
        herkunft - origin
        
        
